502
00:32:26,920 --> 00:32:28,490
You're back?

503
00:32:29,270 --> 00:32:31,530
What did Mi buy again?

504
00:32:31,530 --> 00:32:33,580
Dou sent this to us.

505
00:32:37,640 --> 00:32:38,750
What is it?

506
00:32:38,750 --> 00:32:41,150
I'm guessing Yunnan's delicacies.

507
00:32:41,150 --> 00:32:42,920
Let me have a look.

508
00:32:43,880 --> 00:32:46,309
We've bought them before.

509
00:32:46,310 --> 00:32:47,590
Neither of us enjoy such things.

510
00:32:47,590 --> 00:32:50,749
Tell the kids to stop wasting money.

511
00:32:50,750 --> 00:32:51,640
You don't like such things?

512
00:32:51,640 --> 00:32:53,640
You were gorging yourself on them.

513
00:32:53,640 --> 00:32:57,240
If neither of us eats the food, it'll go to waste.

514
00:32:57,240 --> 00:32:59,860
You even lied about how delicious it was.

